      *
      * LEC
      *
      *  get lot size from kanban master file....
     C           K#AAMP    SETGTAAHTL06
     C           *IN50     DOUEQ*ON
     C           K#AAMP    REDPEAAHTL06                  50
      *
     C           L6SKJY    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           *IN50     IFEQ *OFF
